sentence: what is the lowest point of all states through which the colorado river runs through ?
sentence-with-vars: what is the lowest point of all states through which the river0 runs through ?
sql: select highlow.lowest_point from highlow where highlow.state_name in ( select river.traverse from river where river.river_name = ' colorado ' ) order by highlow.lowest_elevation limit 1 ;
sql-with-vars: select highlow.lowest_point from highlow where highlow.state_name in ( select river.traverse from river where river.river_name = ' river0 ' ) order by highlow.lowest_elevation limit 1 ;
